Package foldocml

Provides a clean API interface to MECUREO services, intended to be used for machine learning

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DistanceFunc An interface for distance functions for nodes that are common between two models being compared
 

Class Summary
AveragedSearchPenalty This SearchPenalty averages the penalty over the number of nodes disjoint
AvgNormSearchPenalty This SearchPenalty averages and normalises the penalties
Connection This class provides the API to the MECUREO toolset
DiffDistance Distance function returning difference in node  weights
DTester O(n) tester for a basic comparison
NormalisedSearchPenalty This SearchPenalty normalises each shortest distance over the maximum and all disjoint nodes
PenaltyFunc A Superclass for Penalty Functions - to return a penalty multiplier to the distance result for common nodes, based on the nodes that are disjoint
SearchPenalty A Penalty function that uses the original ontology to determine 'closeness' of any node not in one of the graphs being compared to the other graph
Similarity FOLDOC Machine Learning Comparison class - to generate and contain the results of a compare algorithm
SpanSimilar A Similarity class based on the Minimum Spanning Tree similiarity
Tester Tester for all similarity functions
WeightedSpanSimilar In Development: a Similarity function to attempt a weighting on minimum spanning tree similarity
 

Package foldocml Description

Provides a clean API interface to MECUREO services, intended to be used for machine learning
